		<description>A small bundle of anima tree leaves, psychically animated to perform simple tasks. Has a limited lifespan before the energy animating it dissipates.</description>
		<statBases>
			<MoveSpeed>5.9</MoveSpeed>
			<Flammability>0.75</Flammability>
			<ToxicResistance>1</ToxicResistance>
			<PsychicSensitivity>0</PsychicSensitivity>
